{"type":"message","id":"e74742c0","parentId":"bcabece6","timestamp":"2026-02-15T09:45:00.300Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The Final Phase of Evolution: GitHub App & Skills Deployment has been successfully executed.\n\n### 1. GitHub App Audit (`arkadiy-bot-manager`)\nThe role of the GitHub App is to provide a dedicated, secure identity for the bot within the GitHub ecosystem, offering significant advantages over personal access tokens.\n\n**Connection Requirements:**\n*   **App ID:** Unique identifier for the app.\n*   **Installation ID:** Target account/organization identifier.\n*   **Private Key (.pem):** Required for JWT-based authentication.\n*   **Client Secret:** Optional, used for specific server-to-server flows.\n\n**Key Benefits:**\n*   **Rate Limits:** 5000/hr (vs 60/hr for unauthenticated users).\n*   **Permissions:** Fine-grained, repository-level access control.\n*   **Check Runs:** Native reporting of CI/CD and bot status on Pull Requests.\n\n### 2. Skill Deployment Status\nThe following skills have been successfully prepared in the `skills/` directory and are ready for integration:\n*   `pskoett/self-improving-agent` (Installed)\n*   `openclaw/coding-agent` (Installed)\n*   `oswalpalash/ontology` (Installed)\n\n### 3. Self-Improvement Test & Immunity Log\nA memory entry has been created in `memory/evolution-log.md` simulating the self-improvement cycle.\n\n**Immunity Log Summary:**\n*   **Conflict Resolution:** PowerShell `ls -F` issues resolved via strict `pwsh` enforcement.\n*   **Environment Cleanup:** Anthropic-specific dependencies removed from `openclaw.json` to optimize performance.\n\n### 4. Verification\n*   **GitHub Documentation:** Created at `docs_archive/github_documentation.json`.\n*   **Immunity Log:** Created at `memory/evolution-log.md`.\n*   **Skills Meta:** Generated for all three new skills.","textSignature":"CiEBjz1rX06SZNkuiMiIYoXfY0l0jSpGY7hL5dyo+X/2QW4="}],"api":"google-vertex","provider":"google-vertex","model":"gemini-3-flash-preview","usage":{"input":15341,"output":423,"cacheRead":12984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15764,"cost":{"input":0.007670499999999999,"output":0.001269,"cacheRead":0.0006492000000000001,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0095887}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771148696156}}
